---
title: CI/CD Pipeline — Automated Release
theme: dark-flow
---
flowchart LR
    codePush([Code Push])
    codePush --> lint[Lint and Format]
    lint -->|pass| unitTest[Run Unit Tests]
    lint -->|fail| lintFail[Notify Lint Failed]
    unitTest -->|pass| dockerBuild[Docker Build]
    unitTest -->|fail| testFail[Notify Tests Failed]
    dockerBuild --> secScan{Security Scan}
    secScan -->|clean| staging([Deploy Staging])
    secScan -->|issues| holdReview[Hold for Review]
    staging -.-> smokeTest[Smoke Tests]
    smokeTest -->|pass| prod([Deploy Production])
    smokeTest -->|fail| rollback[Rollback]
    holdReview --> secScan
